# Class: cpanm
# ===========================
#
# Full description of class cpanm here.
#
# Parameters
# ----------
#
# * `mirror`
# A CPAN mirror to use to retrieve App::cpanminus. This is passed to
# `cpanm` as `--from`, meaning that only this mirror will be used.
#
# Examples
# --------
#
# @example
#    include cpanm
#
# @example
#    class {'cpanm':
#      mirror =>  'http://mirror.my.org/cpan/',
#    }
#
# Authors
# -------
